dct_title_s: Geologic map of eastern Santa Cruz Island, Santa Barbara, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology east Santa Cruz Island C & D quadrangles-DF-78
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared with the support and cooperation of the Santa Cruz Island Foundation, Santa Barbara, California."
Includes 2 cross-sections, location map, note on sources of geology, ill., and 11 aerial photos.
Index map and correlation chart on verso.
